<%- include("header.ejs") %>

<div
    class="w-full text-center flex items-center justify-between lg:justify-center gap-4 px-2 lg:px-0"
>
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img
            src="/images/logo.png"
            alt="Infinity Arcade"
            class="w-6 lg:w-8 opacity-60"
        />
        <div
            href="/"
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-400 text-transparent bg-clip-text text-center py-4 text-xs lg:text-sm opacity-60 tracking-wider inline-block"
        >
            Infinity Arcade
        </div>
    </a>
</div>

<div
    class="container mx-auto text-white max-w-4xl my-4 mt-20 px-4 flex flex-col gap-8"
>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold my-4 text-blue-500">
        Frequently Asked Questions
    </h1>
    <div class="pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-blue-300">What is Infinity Arcade?</h2>
        <div class="prose py-2 flex flex-col gap-6">
            <p>Infinity Arcade is an experiment in AI and game design.</p>
            <ul class="ml-4 md:ml-6 text-white">
                <li class="flex gap-4 items-center py-1">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-white"></div>
                    ChatGPT generates game concepts and the game engine
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-4 items-center py-1">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-white"></div>
                    StableDiffusion generates the game art
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                The big idea is a sufficiently advanced LLM (like ChatGPT), can
                replace a text-game engine. Learn more at
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://themaximalist.com/infinityarcade/"
                    >Infinity Arcade and Sparks of Generative Video Games</a
                >.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-blue-300">Is Infinity Arcade free?</h2>
        <div class="prose py-2 flex flex-col gap-6">
            <p>
                Infinity Arcade is free to play, and I'll do my best to keep it
                that way. The site may have ads in the future.
            </p>
            <p>
                You can
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://infinityarcade.com/pro"
                    >Go Pro</a
                >
                for $8 to unlock extra features, stay ad free and support the
                site.
            </p>
            <p>
                Also Infinity Arcade is
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://github.com/themaximal1st/InfinityArcade"
                    >open source</a
                >
                so you can download it to your computer and play any way you
                want.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-blue-300">How do I generate a video game?</h2>
        <div class="prose py-2 flex flex-col gap-6">
            <p>
                The easiest way to generate a video game is to head to
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://infinityarcade.com/generate"
                    >https://infinityarcade.com/generate</a
                >
                and a random game will be created.
            </p>
            <p>
                Infinity Arcade has a cool feature where you can type
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://infinityarcade.com/a game where you create a game on infinity arcade"
                    >https://infinityarcade.com/anything you want</a
                >
                and a game about that will be generated.
            </p>
            <p>
                You can also create a game from a URL
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://infinityarcade.com/https://infinityarcade.com"
                    >https://infinityarcade.com/http://example.com</a
                >
                and a game will be created from the content of the website.
            </p>
            <p>
                Finally, there are even more advanced ways to create games, by
                modifying the game prompts. Learn
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://infinityarcade.com/articles/how-to-create-a-vide-game"
                    >how to create any video game you want</a
                >
                on Infinity Arcade.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-blue-300">Who made Infinity Arcade?</h2>
        <div class="prose py-2 flex flex-col gap-6">
            <p>
                Infinity Arcade was made by
                <a
                    class="text-blue-100 underline"
                    href="https://themaximalist.com"
                    >The Maximalist</a
                >.
            </p>
            <p>
                Read
                <a class="text-blue-100 underline" href="/about">about</a>
                to learn more.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
